---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Content from "../../layouts/Content.astro";
const pageScript = "/js/pages/generators/uuid-guid.js";
---
<Layout title="UUID and GUID Generator | TechRegistry"><Content title="UUID and GUID Generator" titleTag="Generator" starCount="6.1k stars" usageCount="10.5k uses today" version="v2.7.1" statusText="All Systems Operational" freeLabel="100% Free" privacyLabel="Client-Side Only" breadcrumbs={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "UUID and GUID Generator" }]}><div class="tool-page-shell" id="tool-page-root"><div class="card"><div class="card-body"><div class="tool-toolbar"><button id="tool-load-sample" class="btn btn-outline-light btn-sm" type="button">Load Sample</button><button id="tool-clear" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm" type="button">Clear</button><button id="tool-run" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" type="button">Generate</button></div><div class="tool-field-grid mt-3 mb-3"><div><label class="form-label" for="uuid-version">Version</label><select id="uuid-version" class="form-select" data-tool-field="version"><option value="v4">UUID v4</option><option value="v1">UUID v1</option></select></div><div><label class="form-label" for="uuid-count">Count</label><input id="uuid-count" class="form-control" data-tool-field="count" value="5" /></div></div><div id="tool-status" class="tool-status">Ready.</div><div class="mt-3"><pre id="tool-output" class="tool-code-output"></pre></div></div></div><div class="card tool-details-card"><div class="card-header"><h3 class="card-title">About This UUID and GUID Generator</h3></div><div class="card-body"><p>This UUID and GUID generator creates unique identifiers for database rows, API resources, test fixtures, distributed systems, logs, and event-driven workflows.</p><p>Use it when you need copy-ready UUID v4 values for random identifiers or UUID v1-style values for time-based test scenarios, all generated directly in the browser.</p><ul class="tool-detail-list"><li>Supports UUID v1 and UUID v4 output modes.</li><li>Generates multiple identifiers in one run for bulk fixtures and sample data.</li><li>Useful for backend, frontend, database, API, and QA workflows.</li></ul><div class="tool-points"><a class="tool-point" href="https://github.com/uuidjs/uuid" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"><i class="fa-solid fa-link"></i>Powered by uuid</a></div></div></div></div></Content></Layout><script type="module" src={pageScript}></script>
